CatDescriptText: Cutline of possible related image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, November 15, 1938, pg. unknown, reads: "William A. Harris, Jr., son of the well known sportsman of Pittsburgh, Pa., 'Woogie' Harris.  Young master Harris seems to be definitely heading towards the popularity his dad now enjoys."
TitMainTitle: William Harris III, and young woman, wearing formal clothing posed holding hands or dancing in Loendi Club
